Package dev.tillmann.caylus.cli

package dev.tillmann.caylus.cli
Provides command line user interface. Allows for user interaction with the caylus game. Works on the principle of the model actively requesting the user for input. Also, it provides command line visualization of the game state to the user, so he can make his decisions easier.
